('1','23','5','64','Nice Work!','Thank you very much for providing this wonderful theme which provides all the features you may need it is an integrated template :) Full support is also provided. They have wonderful support :)',NULL,'5','1','0','2020-04-28 03:45:34'),
('2','34','6','73','Very good','The Feature and options of customization are amazing. buy this theme without any research. The team is very helpful and the output of the theme is very user friendly.',NULL,'4','1','0','2020-05-05 08:08:26'),
('3','34','5','64','Nice Work!','\r\n\r\nWe love this theme, it has every feature that a fashion store would need. The support that Promokit gives is beyond 5 stars. Even on buys weekends they still reply to support tickets. They have been beyond helpful to us.\r\n\r\nThank you so much for the awesome theme and support.\r\n',NULL,'5','1','0','2020-05-26 08:39:37'),
('4','46','0','85','Good!','The Theme is incredible good and clean with a really good documentation.\r\nThe Tech support is the best part of all. Fast and accurate. Most important of all .... they will answer to all questions even If some of them could sound too \"stupid/newbie\".\r\nRecommended!\r\n','eliasthanos','3','1','0','2020-06-02 07:42:15');
